---
title: Trainer Notes
layout: layouts/pokeBase.njk
customcss: "/assets/css/shrines/pokemon/me.css"
permalink: /shrines/pokemon/me/
---

<section class="trainer-hero">
  <img class="poke-hero-sticker poke-hero-sticker--top-right poke-hero-sticker--medium"
       src="/assets/imgs/pokemon/graphics/save-file.png"
       alt=""
       aria-hidden="true">

  <img class="poke-hero-sticker poke-hero-sticker--bottom-left poke-hero-sticker--small"
       src="/assets/imgs/pokemon/graphics/frog-sticker.png"
       alt=""
       aria-hidden="true">

  <div class="trainer-hero__copy">
    <p class="trainer-kicker">A little trainer note</p>
    <h1>Violet's Trainer Notes</h1>
    <p>
      A save-file style page for my Pokémon history, favourite eras, shiny dreams,
      hoarding habits, and all the tiny things that make Pokémon feel like home.
    </p>
  </div>

  <aside class="trainer-card">
    <div class="trainer-card__top">
      <span>TRAINER CARD</span>
      <strong>VIOLET</strong>
    </div>

    <dl class="trainer-card__stats">
      <div>
        <dt>Region energy</dt>
        <dd>Kanto / Hoenn</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Favourite era</dt>
        <dd>FR/LG + Emerald</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Play style</dt>
        <dd>Overlevelled and cosy</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Current mode</dt>
        <dd>Safari Week prep</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </aside>
</section>

<section class="trainer-section">
  <div class="trainer-section__heading">
    <p class="trainer-kicker">Trainer notes</p>
    <h2>About my Pokémon brain</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="trainer-note-grid">
    <article class="trainer-note">
      <span class="trainer-note__icon">🌿</span>
      <h3>FR/LG kid forever</h3>
      <p>
        FireRed and LeafGreen are peak comfort Pokémon to me. The chunky GBA UI,
        Kanto routes, simple team building, and Safari Zone chaos all hit perfectly.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="trainer-note">
      <span class="trainer-note__icon">💚</span>
      <h3>Emerald enjoyer</h3>
      <p>
        Hoenn is one of my favourite Pokémon moods: secret bases, water routes,
        Battle Frontier dreams, and that cosy Gen 3 feeling.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="trainer-note">
      <span class="trainer-note__icon">🎒</span>
      <h3>Item hoarder</h3>
      <p>
        I will pick up every hidden item, save every rare candy for “later,” and
        somehow still end the game with a bag full of things I refused to use.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="trainer-note">
      <span class="trainer-note__icon">✨</span>
      <h3>Shiny dreams</h3>
      <p>
        Shinies are becoming their own proper archive now: catches, hunts, phases,
        Safari Week finds, and little stories attached to each sparkle.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="trainer-section trainer-section--save">
  <div class="trainer-section__heading">
    <p class="trainer-kicker">Save file</p>
    <h2>Current Pokémon goals</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="save-file">
    <article>
      <span class="save-file__label">Now playing</span>
      <strong>LeafGreen</strong>
      <p>Building a strong team and pushing toward the Safari Zone for Safari Week.</p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <span class="save-file__label">Current hunt mood</span>
      <strong>Preparation arc</strong>
      <p>Levelling, routing, catching, and setting up the kind of save file future me will thank me for.</p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <span class="save-file__label">Collection goal</span>
      <strong>One source of truth</strong>
      <p>The shiny log now feeds the website properly, so pages do not need manual updates everywhere.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="trainer-section">
  <div class="trainer-section__heading">
    <p class="trainer-kicker">Favourite things</p>
    <h2>Permanent party members</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="fav-grid">
    <div class="fav-chip">Bulbasaur line</div>
    <div class="fav-chip">GBA sprites</div>
    <div class="fav-chip">Safari Zone</div>
    <div class="fav-chip">Physical games</div>
    <div class="fav-chip">Cute merch</div>
    <div class="fav-chip">Overlevelling</div>
    <div class="fav-chip">Secret bases</div>
    <div class="fav-chip">Shiny stories</div>
  </div>
</section>


{% if pokemonPhotos.trainer and pokemonPhotos.trainer.length %}
<section class="trainer-section">
  <div class="trainer-section__heading">
    <p class="trainer-kicker">Memory card</p>
    <h2>Trainer photos</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="pokemon-photo-grid">
    {% for photo in pokemonPhotos.trainer %}
      <figure class="pokemon-photo-card">
        <img src="{{ photo.url }}" alt="{{ photo.alt }}" loading="lazy">
        <figcaption>{{ photo.caption }}</figcaption>
      </figure>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}
